{"tid":1540337,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［請廣傳］不分黃藍，教你擊破「袋住先」謬論","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:23:25.000Z","uid":60845,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"887677bbb435be02a4bd479dfc1d7aa1cd28ea73","tid":1540337,"uid":60845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:18:23.000Z","msg":"以下<span style=\"color: red;\">僅利用公開既事實作邏輯推論</span>，<br />\n不涉及任何未知事實及陰謀論。<br />\n我唔識整圖，同意既<span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎自行配圖作文宣</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一、立即實行真普選</strong><br />\n林鄭今日的我，打到昨日的我<br />\n撤回一個已經「壽終正寢」既修訂<br />\n咁而家究竟係要殺一個死人吖<br />\n定係個人根本一直活著？<br />\n<br />\n咁樣代表由小圈子選舉推出離既林鄭班子<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">毫無誠信、管治威信</span><br />\n因此要<span style=\"color: red;\">立即實行真普選</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>二、成立獨立調查委員會</strong><br />\n監警會主席梁定邦先前公開呼籲<br />\n「政府不應排除成立獨立調查委員會」<br />\n不過今日林鄭係<span style=\"color: red;\">不撤換監警會主席</span>既情況底下<br />\n將<span style=\"color: red;\">堅決反對成立獨委會既余黎青萍</span>安插入去<br />\n<br />\n咁是否代表監警會主席既領導將會被架空？<br />\n監警會<span style=\"color: red;\">內部既口徑都不一致</span><br />\n公眾何從相信監警會可以發揮其作用？<br />\n因此要<span style=\"color: red;\">成立獨立調查委員會</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>三、收回暴動定義</strong><br />\n林鄭班子多次指暫緩修例已是回應訴求<br />\n「撤回」及「壽終正寢」只係字眼分別<br />\n今日同樣<span style=\"color: red;\">願意放下面子</span><br />\n回應民情<span style=\"color: red;\">使用撤回字眼</span><br />\n<br />\n而林鄭亦曾講過，<span style=\"color: red;\">法律程序上並無「暴動定性」</span><br />\n即是此不過一樣為字眼問題<br />\n為何放低左邊面，就不放右邊？<br />\n因此要<span style=\"color: red;\">收回暴動定義</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>四、釋放被捕義士</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最後呢個只寫俾同路人睇</span><br />\n各位和理非們，將心比己<br />\n想象你都係勇武派兄弟<br />\n拉左傷左死左咁多人<br />\n如果只係撤回大家就收手<br />\n唔再爭取釋放義士<br />\n將來再醞釀大型社運既時候<br />\n你仲肯唔肯出離先？<br />\n咁今次<span style=\"color: red;\">就會係最後一次架啦</span><br />\n因此要<span style=\"color: red;\">釋放被捕義士</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">結論：五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fd2507adff43d9f96cab792a8526811644615425","tid":1540337,"uid":60845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:19:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbd438a5b880cadfaa87ce12975b0eab24353dc3","tid":1540337,"uid":60845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:20:39.000Z","msg":"無論藍絲定手足<br />\n再質疑點解唔袋住先既時候<br />\n大家識點答未？"},{"pid":"9330bf8cab2eaf3b5e8093a9bfdf22d94fc9ed01","tid":1540337,"uid":60845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:21:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70d7e26c562c54d169272beef577a5742ee1aee6","tid":1540337,"uid":60845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"738b061a579d0c64c4cd5a59b359648b5a11f712","tid":1540337,"uid":77532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:27:04.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;我唔想十年之後 又出條新例<br />\n到我啲仔女出去比人打&rdquo;<br />\nin case 對長輩"},{"pid":"5b4a1b1179565893c0707b12a7ba24e391a487cc","tid":1540337,"uid":51618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e93ecd6a981c803f39d0b991c5551ca273a72c","tid":1540337,"uid":60845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0c2a5067b66a994a7569fb30899923a2cde5e791","tid":1540337,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:36.000Z","msg":"全面抵制藍色餐廳<br />\n一齊打經濟戰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.289809900000016%252C114.1965917%26z%3D17&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbndT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=968aff8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?